data.description: REDUCED!!! Check out this stunningly beautiful and private property east of Temecula Wine Country! This perfectly situated home is located on a paved road for easy access AND features stunning views of the surrounding hill while offering an amazing level of privacy. If you're looking for the most convenient place to hide away...this is it! This manufactured home built in 2009 sits on approx. 7.3 acres fully fenced. Solar is paid in full. Enjoy panoramic views from the wrap around deck and with custom built deck and gazebo. The oversized living room leads to the formal dining room and spacious kitchen. This home has 2 bedrooms, an office area and a utility room for storage. Relax in the enclosed deck/room off of the primary bedroom which has a spa ready to enjoy the mountain views. This property includes 2 wells, a water softener system, 2 RV hook ups, 2 security gates with remotes, a separate outbuilding/workshop 18'x32', a greenhouse and an animal pen and chicken coop ready for your own farm animals. If you got toys and gear to store...this place has you covered. Want to do some farming and have small animals...heck, even some Big animals? This property can handle it! Just minutes from Temecula without crazy home prices, this retreat is the ideal location for you to live away from all hustle and bustle of the city.
